thread.title: Kelsey Cotter

author: Kelsey Cotter
title: Kelsey Cotter
text: I have been working with the Five9 program for about 8 months now and I really enjoy so many aspects of it. I am able to pull such a wide variety of reports. If I ever am having trouble with something, I am able to call them with ease, and they are able to assist me in getting my issues resolved. They do a great job following up with issues as well. The program itself hardly ever gives me problems, and is very user friendly. I would recommend this company to others.
